        <header>Granzial Sports</header>
        <p>This project was conceived as an integrated space for sports activities for the residents of commune 2. It connects the existing sports fields to spaces adapted for passive recreation. It is intended to consolidate the area’s potential as a recreation zone. It includes the building of the Popular Sports School, the relocation and improvement of the multisport court, and urbanist works along the access roads, Calle 102 and 102b. There are approximately 500,000 beneficiaries from the neighborhoods of Santo Domingo Savio Number 1, Popular, and Moscú Number 2.</p>
    </article>
